name: Puti

readme:
typlog-puti

A Typlog theme for Blog. It's designed by @hi-caicai and originally used in his blog 菩提树下. Typlog has been granted the permission to transplant the design into Typlog's theme gallery and it is free to use for Typlog users.

Thanks

Applauds to @hi-caicai for the original work.
